{
  "page": "Arnell",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the Archmaester, see <a href=\"/index.php/Arnel\" title=\"Arnel\">Arnel</a>. For the Kingslander, see <a href=\"/index.php/Arneld\" title=\"Arneld\">Arneld</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/50px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/75px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/100px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Arnell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/50px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/75px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/100px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\nUnknown <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\">Fossoway</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Arnell</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> and a brother of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>. His mother was a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\">green-apple Fossoway</a>, but it is unknown if he is a legitimate son or a <a href=\"/index.php/Bastardy\" title=\"Bastardy\">bastard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arnell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arnell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Arnell is sent by <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Night&#39;s Watch\">Lord Commander</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">Jeor Mormont</a> as an ambassador to <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a>. Lord Mormont considered sending <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a>, on account of his father <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">Lord</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Randyll_Tarly\" title=\"Randyll Tarly\">Randyll Tarly</a>'s high position in Renly's councils. He sent Arnell because he was considerably more steady than Sam and was kin to the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\">green-apple Fossoways</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is not known if he reaches his destination before Renly's death, nor what has happened to him since.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arnell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p> I'll send Ser Arnell. He's a deal steadier, and his mother was one of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\">green-apple Fossoways</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">Jeor Mormont</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arnell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" col